{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_06_02",
  "title": "白石千紗 2話 自分の歩幅で",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ？　元気がないようだが\n新しいユニットがうまくいっていないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong? You seem down.\nIs the new unit not going well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、ユニットは順調なんですけど\n私が大人っぽくなるのがうまくいかなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ the unit is doing fine.\nIt's just that I'm struggling to become more mature…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（まだ諦めてなかったのか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She hasn't given up yet…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "最近は寮でもたまにスリクスさんの真似をして\n大人っぽく振る舞ってるんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ even at the dorm‚ I've been trying to imitate\nIIIX-san occasionally and act more mature…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "それを見たみんなから「大丈夫？　悩みがあるなら\n相談に乗るよ」って心配されちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But everyone sees through it and asks‚ \"Are you okay?\nIf you have any worries‚ I'm here to listen‚\" so they're worried about me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "誰も私が大人っぽくなったと思ってくれないんです\nどうしたら大人っぽくなれるんだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No one believes that I've become more mature.\nI wonder what I can do to become more mature…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗はどうしてそんなに大人っぽくなりたいんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do you want to become more mature‚ Chisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "それは……子供っぽいって言われると\nなんだか成長してないって言われてるみたいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… When people say I'm childish‚\nit feels like they're saying I haven't grown up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "私だって少しは成長したつもりです。でもまだ足りない\n私はもっと変わりたい……先に進みたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I do feel like I've grown up a bit. But it's not enough.\nI want to change more… I want to move forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか、千紗が大人っぽくなりたいのは）\n（成長したいという思いの表れなのか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I see‚ the reason Chisa want to be more mature is）\n（her desire to grow up more……）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗、後でオフィスに来てくれないか？\n見せたいものがあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Chisa‚ could you come to the office later?\nI have something to show you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5401161443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夕方",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡThat evening",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 77.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "それで……私に見せたいものってなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… what is it that you want to show me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "実は以前、ライブに来てくれたファンに\nアンケートをとったことがあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ there was a time when fans who\ncame to our live concert filled out a questionnaire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのアイドルで誰のどういうところが好きか\n書いてもらったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They wrote about which aspects of\nHoshimi Pro's idols they liked.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、そこにあるアンケート用紙の束には\n私のことが好きって書いてあるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that questionnaire paper over there\nsaying they like me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。千紗のどんなところを好きになったのか\nファンの声を読んでみてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Take a look at what they had to\nsay about you‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4166.666666699995,
          "startTime": 108.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、ええと……「千紗ちゃんが\nひたむきに頑張る姿を見て勇気をもらった」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… Okay… \"Chisa-chan's\ndiligent efforts give me courage when I see them.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "「引っ込み思案な自分を変えようと努力しているのが\n見ていて応援したくなる」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"I want to support her because\nshe's trying to change her shy self.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6860505603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "「一番大人しそうなのに誰よりも頑張ってるところが\n好き。成長を見守っていきたい」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Even though she seems the quietest‚ I love how she works\nharder than anyone. I want to watch her grow.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "分かるか？\nみんな、ありのままの頑張る千紗が好きなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See?\nEveryone likes the real‚ hardworking Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "ありのままの私が好き……\n頑張る私を応援して、成長を見守ってくれてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They like the real me…\nSupporting me as I work hard and grow…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "……私、不安だったんです。不器用で才能もなくて\n練習しても思うように上達出来なくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I was worried. I'm clumsy‚ without talent‚ and\neven when I practice‚ I don't seem to improve as I'd like…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "自分はちゃんと成長出来てるのか……\nちゃんと大人になれるのかいつも不安だったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Am I really growing?\nCan I really become an adult? I've always been anxious about it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それでいいんですね。ありのままの私で……\n急いで大人にならなくてもいいんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it seems okay to be myself. Just the way I am…\nI don't need to force myself to be mature.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "無理して背伸びしなくていい。気負わずに自然体で\n自分のペースで大人になればいいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to force yourself. Just be natural and\ngo at your own pace to become an adult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "……私、早く大人にならなきゃって焦っていたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I was rushing to become an adult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.7666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "それが私らしくないって\n言われるまで気付かないなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't realize that it was not\nbeing myself until I was told…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "私より、いつも応援してくれてるファンのみんなの方が\n私のことを分かってるのかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe the fans who always support me\nunderstand me better than I do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.682327548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
