      "text": "（今日のライブは大盛況だ。千紗も年長者らしく）\n（落ち着いてパフォーマンス出来ているな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Today's concert is a great success. As the oldest‚ Chisa is）\n（composed and performing well.）",
