      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "ライブも大成功だったし、今夜は思い切り楽しむといい\nただし、夜更かしは厳禁だぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since the live was a great success‚ enjoy tonight to the fullest.\nBut remember‚ no staying up late.",
